name: isolated feminism
description:
Feminism has also come under a variety of attacks. The main problem with feminism is the vastness and undefined nature of the movement, which includes the struggle for the protection of gay rights, the issue of fidelity, violence against women, and a whole range of other marital issues, which are by their very nature very complex and important issues that significantly shaped the early 20th century and are still relevant today.


Across the world, women’s feminism will be a silent victim of the Coronavirus pandemic.

Opus #women
